<li><a href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&amp;_udi=B6VFR-4R2HKM6-2&amp;_user=10&amp;_rdoc=1&amp;_fmt=&amp;_orig=search&amp;_sort=d&amp;view=c&amp;_acct=C000050221&amp;_version=1&amp;_urlVersion=0&amp;_userid=10&amp;md5=cba0c7e320e34374ef0974fdc963aad5" class="external text" title="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&amp;_udi=B6VFR-4R2HKM6-2&amp;_user=10&amp;_rdoc=1&amp;_fmt=&amp;_orig=search&amp;_sort=d&amp;view=c&amp;_acct=C000050221&amp;_version=1&amp;_urlVersion=0&amp;_userid=10&amp;md5=cba0c7e320e34374ef0974fdc963aad5" rel="nofollow">Maturity indicators for estimating phytotoxicity in compost-amended soil</a></li>
