<li><a href="http://www.wrap.org.uk/downloads/Introduction_to_BSI_PAS_100-20052.92f2ee6e.2181.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.wrap.org.uk/downloads/Introduction_to_BSI_PAS_100-20052.92f2ee6e.2181.pdf" rel="nofollow">British Standards Institute spec's</a></li>
<li><a href="http://compost.css.cornell.edu/Composting_homepage.html" class="external text" title="http://compost.css.cornell.edu/Composting_homepage.html" rel="nofollow">Cornell University Composting pages</a></li>
</ul>
